WEBVTT

00:00.434 --> 00:01.534
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:01.536 --> 00:02.668
You're Klaus' father?

00:02.670 --> 00:03.936
You can bring me back to life.

00:03.937 --> 00:05.638
Welcome to my hell.

00:05.640 --> 00:06.739
[Gasps]

00:06.741 --> 00:07.773
You're all right.

00:07.775 --> 00:09.074
Have you dreamt of our father?

00:09.076 --> 00:10.376
I saw Mikael.

00:10.378 --> 00:11.877
I've been dreaming of him, too.

00:11.879 --> 00:14.280
Your mother was clearly
a very gifted witch.

00:14.282 --> 00:15.781
Marcel: Any way I do the math,

00:15.783 --> 00:17.416
it ends with me and my guys dead,

00:17.418 --> 00:19.385
so whatever it is you got
coming with the wolves,

00:19.387 --> 00:22.288
just know that I will
fight until I am dead!

00:22.290 --> 00:23.622
Raaaah!

00:23.624 --> 00:25.090
Aah!

00:27.661 --> 00:28.861
Francesca: Nice job.

00:28.863 --> 00:30.029
You saved me the trouble

00:30.031 --> 00:32.898
of killing all these vampires myself.

00:32.900 --> 00:34.466
Aah!

00:34.468 --> 00:36.468
That baby is part witch.

00:36.470 --> 00:39.338
She has to be born first
before she can die.

00:39.340 --> 00:40.372
No!

00:40.374 --> 00:41.507
This the way it had to be.

