01:47.139 --> 01:49.040
Oh!

01:49.042 --> 01:50.542
You feel that?

01:57.416 --> 02:00.018
Right.

02:00.020 --> 02:03.354
I'll leave you to your secret letter then.

02:13.132 --> 02:15.867
Hayley, voice-over: "Dear Zoey..."

02:15.869 --> 02:19.170
"or Caitlin or Angela.

02:19.172 --> 02:22.340
"To my little girl,

02:22.342 --> 02:26.344
"your dad just asked
if this was a love letter.

02:26.346 --> 02:29.447
I guess it kind of is."

02:29.449 --> 02:31.983
[Hayley screaming]

02:31.985 --> 02:34.485
Hayley, voice-over:
"I never got to know my mother.

02:34.487 --> 02:36.354
"I have no idea what she must have felt

02:36.356 --> 02:37.321
when she carried me."

02:37.323 --> 02:38.823
Let go of me, you bitch!

02:41.227 --> 02:43.027
"So I thought I'd write to you

02:43.029 --> 02:45.062
"so that you could know how happy I am

02:45.064 --> 02:47.698
"at this very moment,

02:47.700 --> 02:49.233
"how much your father and I

02:49.235 --> 02:50.534
can't wait to meet you."

02:50.536 --> 02:53.738
[Panting]

02:53.740 --> 02:55.940
"And I want to make you a promise,

02:55.942 --> 02:59.477
"3 things that you
will have that I never did...

02:59.479 --> 03:01.745
"A safe home,

03:01.747 --> 03:03.581
"someone to tell you that they love you

03:03.583 --> 03:06.116
"every single day,

03:06.118 --> 03:10.487
and someone to fight
for you no matter what."

03:10.489 --> 03:11.855
Aah!

03:11.857 --> 03:14.024
"In other words, a family.

03:14.026 --> 03:15.592
"So there you go, baby girl.

03:15.594 --> 03:18.195
"The rest we're gonna
have to figure out together.

03:18.197 --> 03:20.931
I love you, your mom."

03:20.933 --> 03:23.434
[Moaning]

03:25.737 --> 03:28.772
You should know this brings me no joy.

03:28.774 --> 03:30.240
I promise I'll make it quick.

03:30.242 --> 03:32.109
[Screaming]

03:32.111 --> 03:33.510
Let's begin, shall we?

03:33.512 --> 03:34.912
