03:49.861 --> 03:53.163
Cami?

03:53.165 --> 03:55.699
Oh, God. What happened?

03:55.701 --> 03:57.234
Klaus.

03:57.236 --> 03:59.536
They fought, and he got bit.

03:59.538 --> 04:00.937
Marcel.

04:00.939 --> 04:02.973
It's ok. I gave as good as I got,

04:02.975 --> 04:05.475
