04:10.448 --> 04:13.183
You fought Klaus.

04:13.185 --> 04:14.484
Did he bleed?

04:14.486 --> 04:16.486
I got him pretty good, yeah.

04:16.488 --> 04:18.622
Where?

04:23.828 --> 04:25.328
Unh!

04:37.775 --> 04:40.977
Venez sanguis. Venez sanguis.

04:40.979 --> 04:42.378
Venez sanguis. Venez...

04:42.380 --> 04:45.515
Uh, Davina.

04:45.517 --> 04:46.516
What the hell?

04:46.518 --> 04:47.750
Josh, what are you doing here?

04:47.752 --> 04:49.118
I told you to rest.

04:49.120 --> 04:50.386
I'm fine.

04:50.388 --> 04:51.621
You're gonna start hallucinating soon.

04:51.623 --> 04:53.022
I mean, unless I'm

04:53.024 --> 04:54.490
hallucinating you standing

04:54.492 --> 04:57.226
in the middle of the street
and chanting for no reason.

04:59.764 --> 05:01.898
Wait. Am I?

05:01.900 --> 05:03.566
I'm gonna save you.

05:03.568 --> 05:07.503
I'm gonna save all of you.

05:07.505 --> 05:11.507
Venez sanguis. Venez sanguis.

05:11.509 --> 05:14.744
Venez sanguis. Venez sanguis.

05:14.746 --> 05:18.314
Venez sanguis. Venez sanguis.

05:18.316 --> 05:21.817
Venez sanguis. Venez sanguis.

05:21.819 --> 05:25.421
Venez sanguis. Venez sanguis.

05:25.423 --> 05:28.791
Ok. I am hallucinating.

05:28.793 --> 05:30.192
[Hayley screaming]

05:30.194 --> 05:32.294
Klaus: I will bring hell to your doorstep!

05:32.296 --> 05:33.562
One last push. The baby's almost here.

05:33.564 --> 05:35.031
I will bathe in rivers of your blood!

05:35.033 --> 05:36.365
No, no!

05:36.367 --> 05:37.433
I can see the baby!

05:37.435 --> 05:39.068
Ok. Now push.

05:39.070 --> 05:40.302
Gently, gently.

05:40.304 --> 05:42.371
You will die screaming!

05:42.373 --> 05:44.273
There.

05:44.275 --> 05:46.709
[Hayley gasping]

05:48.545 --> 05:50.746
[Baby coos]

05:53.884 --> 05:56.752
[Crying]

05:59.556 --> 06:01.757
You have a beautiful baby daughter.

06:07.130 --> 06:08.564
We must start the sacrifice

06:08.566 --> 06:10.466
as soon as the moon sets
with the morning sky.

06:10.468 --> 06:14.269
Please. Please can I hold her?

06:19.142 --> 06:21.977
[Baby gurgling]

06:25.748 --> 06:29.017
[Crying]

06:29.019 --> 06:30.652
Oh.

06:32.689 --> 06:34.323
No!

06:39.529 --> 06:42.364
[Baby crying]

06:49.505 --> 06:52.040
[Klaus screaming]

06:52.042 --> 06:53.642
[Crack]

07:04.401 --> 07:06.135
Hayley!

07:18.715 --> 07:20.149
No.

07:46.843 --> 07:48.844
She's gone.

08:01.224 --> 08:03.024
You've been bitten.

08:18.441 --> 08:21.309
There's only enough here for one.

08:21.311 --> 08:24.045
No. This has to be enough!

08:39.461 --> 08:42.697
I... I can't choose.

08:42.698 --> 08:45.033
Please don't make me choose.

08:51.307 --> 08:54.142
Save your friend.

08:54.144 --> 08:56.210
I can take care of the rest of us.

08:56.212 --> 08:57.245
Marcel.

08:57.247 --> 08:58.346
I can't.

08:58.348 --> 08:59.514
Judging by the look of that bite,

08:59.516 --> 09:00.681
you don't have time to argue.

09:00.683 --> 09:02.183
Marcel.

09:02.185 --> 09:05.053
Josh is one of my guys,

09:05.055 --> 09:07.488
and enough of my guys have died today,

09:07.490 --> 09:09.524
so come on.

09:17.466 --> 09:21.002
Mikael: One point for you

09:21.004 --> 09:24.038
and one point for Niklaus.

09:36.685 --> 09:38.452
Cami: Hey.

09:38.454 --> 09:39.754
Where do you think you're going?

09:39.756 --> 09:42.223
To find Klaus, get his blood,

09:42.225 --> 09:44.058
and save as many of my guys as I can.

09:44.060 --> 09:45.426
Wait.

09:47.028 --> 09:49.396
For that, you'll need a weapon,

09:49.398 --> 09:51.966
and it just so happens I have an arsenal.

10:03.812 --> 10:06.280
How?

10:06.282 --> 10:08.215
I was bested.

10:08.217 --> 10:10.250
You were bested?

10:15.457 --> 10:17.758
You...

10:17.760 --> 10:21.528
Were bested?!

10:21.530 --> 10:24.131
My invincible brother?

10:29.837 --> 10:34.074
They took the baby, but there's still time.

10:34.076 --> 10:37.144
We can save her.

10:42.016 --> 10:43.683
The tombs are empty, the
grounds are deserted.

10:43.685 --> 10:45.051
She's not here.

10:45.053 --> 10:46.653
This is the only place they can be.

10:46.655 --> 10:47.954
- We'll keep searching.
- They are not here, Niklaus.

10:47.956 --> 10:49.189
We're wasting time.

10:49.191 --> 10:50.357
Their harvest was here,

10:50.359 --> 10:51.658
the reaping was here.

10:51.660 --> 10:53.126
They are about to perform a ritual

10:53.128 --> 10:54.895
which will feed their
ancestors for centuries,

10:54.897 --> 10:57.864
ancestors who are buried here!

11:03.137 --> 11:05.906
This statue.

11:05.908 --> 11:07.774
We've passed by this 3 times

11:07.776 --> 11:10.443
all whilst going in the same direction.

11:24.158 --> 11:26.860
They have fabricated some kind of illusion.

11:33.267 --> 11:35.368
That's one word for it.

11:57.528 --> 11:59.128
So this is what Kieran was hiding.

11:59.130 --> 12:01.063
More like stockpiling.

12:01.065 --> 12:03.099
From what I can gather,
it's mostly weapons.

12:03.101 --> 12:06.068
Dark objects created by witches.

12:06.070 --> 12:09.438
And co-opted by the humans.

12:09.440 --> 12:11.540
Kieran's been keeping
this a secret for years.

12:11.542 --> 12:13.143
You really sure you want
to show me all this?

12:13.210 --> 12:14.909
You said knowing my uncle's secrets

12:14.911 --> 12:16.745
could get me killed.

12:16.747 --> 12:18.513
What if those same secrets
could save the lives

12:18.515 --> 12:20.315
of my friends?

12:20.317 --> 12:21.683
Look at this.

12:21.685 --> 12:23.017
I learned about it in the LycÃ©e.

12:23.019 --> 12:24.886
It's called the devil's star.

12:24.888 --> 12:27.388
They say one throw
can make a thousand cuts.

12:27.390 --> 12:29.357
A thousand cuts sounds about right.

12:29.359 --> 12:31.526
I need to make Klaus bleed.

12:36.332 --> 12:38.866
[Scrape]

12:38.868 --> 12:39.967
It's ingenious.

12:39.969 --> 12:42.103
I can see them, I can feel them,

12:42.105 --> 12:44.072
and yet they are not real.

12:44.074 --> 12:45.339
There has to be a way.

12:45.341 --> 12:46.808
Even if we could just push through.

12:46.810 --> 12:48.342
What we need to do is focus.

12:48.344 --> 12:49.744
My only focus right now is that child

12:49.746 --> 12:51.646
and her safety, do you understand me?

12:51.648 --> 12:53.347
This, all of this,

12:53.349 --> 12:55.550
this is the world that
you created, Niklaus.

12:55.552 --> 12:56.617
Brother.

12:56.619 --> 12:58.119
All of your scheming,

12:58.121 --> 12:59.820
the enemies that you have
made every single day

12:59.822 --> 13:00.955
