13:00.957 --> 13:02.890
What results did you expect?

13:02.892 --> 13:04.926
That your child would be
born into a happy life,

13:04.928 --> 13:06.694
that the mother would be alive

13:06.696 --> 13:08.029
to know her daughter,

13:08.031 --> 13:09.730
that we could live and thrive

13:09.732 --> 13:11.132
as some sort of family?

13:11.134 --> 13:13.401
That was your fantasy, brother, not mine!

13:13.403 --> 13:14.735
No, brother.

13:14.737 --> 13:17.004
This was our hope.

13:17.006 --> 13:21.809
This was our family's hope,

13:21.811 --> 13:24.545
and now she is gone.

13:24.547 --> 13:25.646
Do you understand?

13:25.648 --> 13:29.383
I... Let this person in.

13:31.019 --> 13:33.888
I let her in.

13:33.890 --> 13:36.090
I don't let people in.

13:36.092 --> 13:38.225
You knew this,

13:38.227 --> 13:40.594
