14:06.187 --> 14:08.088
You can tell your niece

14:08.090 --> 14:12.259
how much you cared for her mother

14:12.261 --> 14:14.228
when we save her.

14:38.119 --> 14:39.619
[Gasps]

14:49.063 --> 14:50.830
Aah!

14:50.832 --> 14:52.332
Push!

14:55.236 --> 14:56.670
No!

14:57.772 --> 14:59.005
[Crying]

15:10.317 --> 15:11.718
The moon has almost faded

15:11.720 --> 15:13.419
