15:27.635 --> 15:28.968
She'll go through with it.

15:28.970 --> 15:30.937
The ancestors promised her her life.

15:30.939 --> 15:32.638
What about their promise to us?

15:32.640 --> 15:34.140
4 harvest girls sacrificed,

15:34.142 --> 15:35.742
4 girls returned,

15:35.744 --> 15:37.076
but her friends hijack it,

15:37.078 --> 15:39.011
