to dress things up a bit.

16:41.776 --> 16:43.409
It's fancy witch speak.

16:43.411 --> 16:45.944
Nexus Vorti... A rare occurrence,

16:45.946 --> 16:48.213
something so infrequent

16:48.215 --> 16:49.848
