26:03.762 --> 26:05.328
You brought me back to kill my son.

26:05.330 --> 26:07.263
I brought you back to punish him,

26:07.265 --> 26:08.865
and you will when I'm ready

26:08.867 --> 26:10.133
and not a minute before.

26:10.135 --> 26:15.004
What... Have... You... Done?

26:16.174 --> 26:17.841
